title: United Kingdom Imports Intra Eu - Railway & Tram Tracks, Signals, Fixings, Etc.
description: Imports Intra Eu - Railway & Tram Tracks, Signals, Fixings, Etc. in the United Kingdom decreased to 44.06 GBP Million in September from 50.75 GBP Million in August of 2022. Imports Intra Eu - Railway & Tram Tracks, Signals, in the United Kingdom averaged 32.78 GBP Million from 1996 until 2022, reaching an all time high of 188.95 GBP Million in September of 2016 and a record low of 2.13 GBP Million in October of 1996. This page includes a chart with historical data for the United Kingdom Imports of Intra EU - Railway & Tram Tracks, Sign.
author: Hm Customs And Excise
